    <div class="comment--content">
      <p>Thanks for the soup! Turned out great for a rainy Tokyo night. Houseguests were pleased. Topped it off with the ginger cake from epicurious that you mentioned in an earlier post (though the more highly rated David Lebovitz version looks amazing too! next time&#8230;) and that topped with whipped cream. Yes! Anything that calls for cream, sign me up&#8230;</p>
