    <div class="comment--content">
      <p>This is a lovely soup recipe &#8211; made it tonight on a cold, grey day and it warmed our family up and brightened our day.  Used the last bit of fresh sage from our herb garden.  Thank you so much for bringing such joy into our day.  </p>
<p>Sharon</p>
